invalid type: string "6\nPrototype-to-Production Gaps Must Be Acknowledged Early\nThe in-memory store, SHA-256 (instead of bcrypt), and single-threaded design are all\nacceptable for a prototype but would be liabilities in production. Explicitly documenting these\ngaps in the README's 'Extending the Prototype' section, rather than ignoring them, created\nUI & Demo Data\nr/lower/digit).\nction.\nÿÿ